%section#wildlife.container.content-section
  .row
    .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2
      %h2.text-center Wildlife
      %p
        The particular habitat of the Chinko allows for an incredible richness of species,
        and puzzling phenomena, making it a hotspot of biodiversity.
      %p
        .image
          = image_tag('wildlife/wild-dog-family.jpg', class: 'img-responsive')
          .image-description
            Wild Dog Family

      %p
        So far we've documented more than 75 mammals (including Wild Dog, Elephant, Lelwell
        Hartebeest, Eastern Giant Eland, Bongo, Lion and Leopard).

      %p
        Explore a selection of these pictures together with our publications online at our
        = succeed '.' do
          = link_to "research platform", "http://research.chinkoproject.com", { target: '_blank' }

      %p
        #wildlife-carousel.owl-carousel
          - %w(oribi-in-savannah-opening warthog leopard-track leopard leopard-in-front-of-camera-trap hartebeest).each do |name|
            .image
              = image_tag('wildlife/'+ name +'.jpg')
              .image-description
                = name.titleize

        :javascript
          $(document).ready(function(){
            $("#wildlife-carousel").owlCarousel({
                items: 1,
                loop: true,
                margin: 10,
                lazyLoad: true,
                merge: true,
                video: true
              });
          });
